copy c/wait to SYS:c/wait
copy c/echo to SYS:c/echo
copy c/more to SYS:c/more
wait 1
Echo " "
Echo "   Kopiere nun die benötigten Fonts !           "
Echo "                             "
Echo "                             "
Echo "   Bitte warten...           "
Echo " "
Wait 3
copy Fonts to SYS:Fonts
copy Fonts/futural to SYS:Fonts/futural
Echo " "
wait 3
Echo " "
Echo " "
Echo "   Kopiere nun die Abspielroutine -Smartplay- und"
Echo "   den Viewer -Fastview- in Dein C-Verzeichnis (SYS) ! "
Echo "   Beide Programme werden benötigt,um Musik und Bilder"
Echo "   der Amiga 4ever abzuspielen/anzuzeigen !"
wait 5
copy c/smart to SYS:c/smart
wait 1
copy c/fv to SYS:c/fv
wait 2
Echo "   Leaving... "
wait 1
